<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        
  .bg {
            animation: slide 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
            background-image: linear-gradient(-60deg, rgb(153, 204, 51) 50%, rgb(255, 213, 0) 50%);
            bottom: 0;
            left: -50%;
            opacity: .5;
            position: fixed;
            right: -50%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .bg2 {
            animation-direction: alternate-reverse;
            animation-duration: 4s;
        }

        .bg3 {
            animation-duration: 5s;
        }

        @keyframes slide {
            0% {
                transform: translateX(-25%);
            }

            100% {
                transform: translateX(25%);
            }
        }

        body{
            
            text-align: center;
        }
        .custom-card{
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 10px rgb(194, 194, 194);
            margin: 10px;
            padding-top: 10px;
            background-color: rgb(250, 243, 227);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .center-title{
            text-align: center;
        }
        .paragraph{
            display: block;
            align-items: center;
            width: 750px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .like{
            color: red;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.555);
            border: solid;
            border-color: red;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .like:hover{            
            background-color:red            
        }
    </style>
    <title>Smoothies</title>
</head>

<body>
    
<div class="bg"></div>
<div class="bg bg2"></div>
<div class="bg bg3"></div>


    <h1 class= "display-3 center-title">Healthy Smoothies App</h1>
    
        <p class="paragraph">
            Even thought they're chock full of nutrients, smoothies don't have to be boring.
            These healthy smoothie recipes are anything but, featuring sweet, colorful frozen fruit
            (and veggies!), unexpected herbs and spices and creamy add-ins like yogurt and banana
            to make the dreamiest sips ever. Plus, smoothies make the best quick breakfasts
            that you can enjoy on the go or as you sit down at your desk.
        </p>
    
    <a href="/add" class="btn btn-primary center-title"> + Add New Smoothie</a>

    <h2 class= "display-6 center-title"> our recipes: </h2>

    <div class="container" >
        <div class="row">
        <% for (let i=0 ;i<smoothies.length; i++) { %>
            <div class="card custom-card" style="width: 18rem;">
                <img src="<%= smoothies[i].photo %>" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title"><%= smoothies[i].name %></h5>
                  <p class="card-text"><%= smoothies[i].level %> </p>
                  <a href="/like/<%= i %> " class="btn btn-secondary like">
                    ‚ù§Ô∏è Like <%= smoothies[i].like %>               
                  </a>                                    
                  <a href="/recipe/<%= i %> " class="btn btn-primary">üìÉ Show Recipe</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>